{"word":"G2158 - εὐσχήμων - euschḗmōn - yoo-skhay'-mone - Comely","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">εὐσχήμων</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">euschḗmōn</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">yoo-skhay'-mone</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Comely</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"கனம்பொருந்திய, இலட்சணமுள்ள, தகுதியான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"1. of elegant figure, shapely, graceful, comely"},{"paragraph":"2. good standing, honorable, influential, wealthy, respectable"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2095 - εὖ - eû - yoo/2095\">G2095</a> and <a href=\"#/G4976 - σχῆμα - schēma - skhay'-mah/4976\">G4976</a>; <i>well formed</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>decorous</i>, <i>noble</i> (in rank): - comely, honourable.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}